@startuml ExamCreationFlow
scale 0.9
autonumber

actor Admin as "Center Admin"
participant UI
participant API
database DB

== Quick Exam Submission Flow ==

Admin -> UI : Open pending dossiers dashboard
UI -> API : GET /pending-dossiers
API -> DB : Fetch pending patients
DB --> API : patients + doctors
API --> UI : Display dossiers list

Admin -> UI : Click "Démarrer examen"
UI -> API : POST /patients/{id}/start-exam
API -> DB : Verify dossier status
DB --> API : Patient + doctor data
API --> UI : Redirect with params
activate UI
UI -> UI : new-exam-autofill.js:\nLoad patient_id & doctor_id from URL
UI -> API : GET /patients, /doctors (load dropdowns)
API --> UI : Lists
deactivate UI

UI --> Admin : Form pre-filled

Admin -> UI : Upload retinal images
Admin -> UI : Submit exam
UI -> API : POST /exams (images + IDs)
activate API
API -> DB : Create exam record
API -> API : Trigger AI inference (async)
API --> UI : Exam created successfully
deactivate API

UI --> Admin : Confirmation

note right of UI
    **Optimization:**
    URL parameters enable instant
    form pre-population without
    manual selection
end note

@enduml
